quran[1]{c,v,t}:
  5,5,"elyevme uhille lekumu-ttayyibat. veta`amu-llezine utu-lkitabe hillul lekum. veta`amukum hillul lehum. velmuhsanatu mine-lmu'minati velmuhsanatu mine-llezine utu-lkitabe min kablikum iza ateytumuhunne ucurahunne muhsinine gayra musafihine vela muttehizi ahdan. vemey yekfur bil'imani fekad habita `ameluh. vehuve fi-l'ahirati mine-lhasirin"
